document.full_text: palestinian rockets struck two cities deep in israel on wednesday, wounding a resident and prompting prime minister benjamin netanyahu to threaten lengthy "exchanges of blows" with the hamas-ruled gaza strip.
document.title: israel braces for flare-up as gazan rockets hit
